{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the dark wilderness of an ancient forest and face the hidden demons who put you to the test. Your mission is clear: collect the secret chalices that the demons have hidden deep within this living, breathing forest. But beware, this forest is no ordinary place. The demons reign here, and they are cursed. They possess the ability to teleport you to other places \u2013 and they use the chalices to do so!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Goal is Clear: Find All the Chalices!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/demon_alive_gif_3.gif?t=1736446709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But the journey won't be easy. First, you must face the dark domains\u2014sinister places where darkness itself seems alive. Here, horror lurks in every shadow, and only with unwavering patience can you endure the trials set by the demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These creatures of the night will do everything in their power to stop you. But know this: if you remain steadfast and survive their assaults, their resistance will falter. Only then, in a moment of reluctant surrender, will they reveal the hidden chalices\u2014unintentionally paving your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/demon_alive_gif_4.gif?t=1736446709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have two essential tools at your disposal: a trusty pistol to protect yourself and a flashlight to pierce the ever-present darkness. Use them wisely, for the shadows are deceptive, and the demons are merciless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you prove both your strength and your patience, the chalices will ultimately belong to you\u2014trophies of your unwavering courage and determination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339100/extras/demon_alive_gif_2.gif?t=1736446709\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Now I ask you: Are you ready to face the games of the demons and claim the chalices for yourself?</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Teleport Mansion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/1e753d53d646aa86d9abca2c3468e4bcad61399a.jpg"},{"name":"Teleport Aksa","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/ffe2372118d247cced5df6115e2c9e8efac28862.jpg"},{"name":"Teleport Forest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/aa9318c0614c29c8969ba9f9e8fc5315dba154df.jpg"},{"name":"First Chalice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/fd1a5d6c6673083c3d3b5f62aee826a54a810f69.jpg"},{"name":"Holy Place","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/b695cc9d85853b038c0f27752c2a778e9049998c.jpg"},{"name":"You killed 100 Demons!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/1c4182daad28e5543ee0fc1bf40c2eb6f8eab0bf.jpg"},{"name":"You have 250 kills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/94408dc27c800f6963512222d8659f27fae57363.jpg"},{"name":"You have reached 500 kills","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/af5c63bcf1dacaa7ae72b88264e14603be7ba3fc.jpg"},{"name":"250 ammunition","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339100/eb1aae0b11a2e14bbbfd89127072238ff1ca3f87.jpg"},{"name":"250 healing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic